{"tid":1261914,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國女團內撕有嚴重？表面閨蜜姐妹花，背地裡卻堪比「甄嬛傳」","createTime":"2019-06-27T12:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T12:45:27.000Z","uid":1086,"like":6,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"edd47e508e70da2e39ed0ee96bbb93ab79d52dcd","tid":1261914,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"隨著韓流目前的流行趨勢的越來越走紅，許多年輕人都開始喜歡韓國的愛豆團體。這些韓國的愛豆也基本都是經過長時間的訓練，不僅僅是包括他們的唱歌表演，在鏡頭前的一舉一動也都進行了相當嚴格的訓練。在相當重視「團魂」的韓國，一個愛豆團體是否有「團魂」也是他們重要圈粉的一點，不過這些愛豆團體可並不止表面上看上去的那麼簡單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/7518084841/641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F7518084841%2F641&h=c4d73219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月29日這天，韓國爆火女子團體blackpink中的兩位成員中被曝出不合，並空降熱搜，引起了熱議。被曝出不合的兩位成員分別是Jennie和來自泰國的Lisa，成員Jennie被質疑霸凌Lisa。在某檔綜藝節目中，Lisa給Jennie脫襪子，而Jennie完全是一幅高高在上的樣子，彷彿Lisa是洗腳婢一樣。在早期的live直播之時，Jennie擋住Lisa霸屏也是家常便飯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/4529588283/641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F4529588283%2F641&h=bf39a7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/9146162223/641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F9146162223%2F641&h=53d143e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然Lisa和Jennie在照片中關係感覺很好，但還是讓人有種說不出的感覺，不得不說萬事不能只看表面了。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/9146164993/641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F9146164993%2F641&h=c1d1ec8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不僅僅是blackpink，周潔瓊在韓國發展時也曾遭受過隊友的排擠。可能是因為人氣高，以及是外國人的原因，周潔瓊在隊內經常是自己一個人走，別人都是三兩成群，而周潔瓊卻孤單一個人。在粉絲見面會上，周潔瓊雖然遭到了隊友們開玩笑式的打鬧，但有一位成員卻非常用力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2b4i8bq/39sn0001525r3orqon02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2b4i8bq%2F39sn0001525r3orqon02.jpg&h=c2800e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=e7pea2/3n01000141o3sr34975r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3De7pea2%2F3n01000141o3sr34975r.jpg&h=577e163c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=3b9qjd9/3n010001436q9ro572op.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3b9qjd9%2F3n010001436q9ro572op.jpg&h=4bfe81c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國最火的女團twice也是如此，成員林娜璉在活動中與成員SANA蓋了同一條防止走光的毯子，可林娜璉卻絲毫沒有顧及SANA，將毯子拽到了自己的一邊，SANA差點走光，也只能無奈的笑笑。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/9146100933/641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F9146100933%2F641&h=0b1bb070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/030415_69516e18ffc2845bb60d8342b21e3618.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F030415_69516e18ffc2845bb60d8342b21e3618.gif&h=a7a92d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/030419_e08f7b4effeb8a193318bd5b5a9c6622.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F030419_e08f7b4effeb8a193318bd5b5a9c6622.gif&h=f88e636e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n生活中的女孩子們也都少不了吵架鬥嘴，更何況這些朝夕相處，還有著隱形的競爭關係的女孩子們了，看上去還真是一出「大戲」，仔細挖掘真是亮點滿滿，雖然表面上「團魂」滿滿，可這些小細節卻無不透露著「心機」。"},{"pid":"c438b0d34ea7659803b8087ed25fa7d767fb1f64","tid":1261914,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"仲以為你又想講RV添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd9f0d4f803bb16666c034801ec83bbeb568e32","tid":1261914,"uid":64476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8965231a48079af93f5be3062469b79c8a0677","tid":1261914,"uid":28808,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:38:37.000Z","msg":"成篇野充斥匪語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e65d57c06feb77a2b575648f3417a26a738e49","tid":1261914,"uid":138138,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/166/16661244.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F166%2F16661244.jpg&h=0f28128f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禾地BP係一隊關係好到可以甘心幫隊長洗腳既組合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5110a84c1acc3b0c39e2f3dc579d538478806a7d","tid":1261914,"uid":1086,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/024709_c54aefde77cc9c0c0a59e0b31d1d8ae0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F024709_c54aefde77cc9c0c0a59e0b31d1d8ae0.gif&h=f65b758d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"916daac8ca2aefaf76fc7a57146635a8ac16f8b3","tid":1261914,"uid":1086,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/024707_b85bae258b1176b34658715f1532b5ac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F024707_b85bae258b1176b34658715f1532b5ac.gif&h=08c28fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/024703_9d8988ef587131bc626bb6eb7a0062d5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F024703_9d8988ef587131b